//         original_desc: "<title level=\"1\" right=\"Action\">[Call to Axis](/Actions.aspx?ID=731) <actions string=\"Free Action\" /></title>\r\n\r\n<traits>\r\n<trait label=\"Fortune\" url=\"/Traits.aspx?ID=76\" />\r\n</traits>\r\n\r\n<column gap=\"tiny\">\r\n\r\n**Source** [The Mwangi Expanse](/Sources.aspx?ID=89) pg. 107 <sup>2.0</sup>\n\n**Frequency** once per day\n\n**Requirements** You are about to attempt a check to [Recall Knowledge](/Actions.aspx?ID=26).\r\n\r\n</column>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nYou call upon the knowledge of Axis to ensure the accuracy of your information. You roll a second time and use the higher result. If you roll a critical failure, you get a failure instead. If you roll a success, you get a critical success instead.",
