//         original_desc: "<title level=\"1\" right=\"Action\">[Selfish Shield](/Actions.aspx?ID=2804) <actions string=\"Reaction\" /></title>\r\n\r\n<traits>\r\n\r\n</traits>\r\n\r\n<column gap=\"tiny\">\r\n\r\n**Source** [Player Core 2](/Sources.aspx?ID=227) pg. 91\n\n**Trigger** An enemy in your champion’s aura damages you\n\n</column>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nYour self-interest keeps you safe. You gain resistance against the triggering damage equal to 2 + half your level, regardless of damage type.<br /> In addition, your Strikes against the triggering creature deal 1 extra spirit damage until the end of your next turn. This extra damage increases to 2 at 9th level and 3 at 16th level.",
