//         original_desc: "<title level=\"1\" right=\"Action\">[Seedpod Spring](/Actions.aspx?ID=1653) <actions string=\"Two Actions\" /></title>\r\n\r\n<traits>\r\n\r\n</traits>\r\n\r\n<column gap=\"tiny\">\r\n\r\n**Source** [Treasure Vault](/Sources.aspx?ID=191) pg. 107 <sup>1.1</sup>\n\n</column>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nA seedpod within the chair bursts and uncoils, releasing a light clump of cottony material. Your rootball chair [Leaps](/Actions.aspx?ID=81) up to 30 feet vertically or horizontally and drifts down, sinking 5 feet for every 5 feet traveled horizontally and causing you to take no [falling damage](/Rules.aspx?ID=402). The cottony material disperses when you land.",
